      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior is absolutely flawless with no scratches, dents, or chips, and the paint retains a deep, factory-fresh shine. Inside, the cabin is pristine with no signs of wear, and all features function perfectly. Mechanically, it is in peak condition with a complete service history, offering a driving experience that is indistinguishable from a new car.",
